events.question:
Oh! Hello again! Are you still trying to get stuff for your… thing?
What are you going to do again? I don’t think you told me. Not that you have to! Privacy and all.

events.choice: I’m actually going on a date later! And yeah, I’m still getting stuff for it.

events.question:
Aw, that’s so sweet! I wish I was going on a date, instead.
Anyways, same thing as before! And please finish up before the monster gets here!
I don’t want to explain to your date that you got flattened by it!

events.choice: Haha, OK. Thanks for looking out for us!
Ok, hopefully the monster will be gone soon! I feel like it might be…
Oh y’know, just hanging out with a friend! I’m almost done getting things, though!

events.question:
Fun! You’re such a good friend for getting all this stuff for them!
Anyways, make sure you’re out of here soon because the monster might come here!
Then your friend will be asking where all the stuff went! Haha, just kidding.

events.choice: Wouldn’t be surprised if she did! Ok, bye!
Ugh, I know right? Anyways, bye!
